## Next Steps (For Deployment)
When deploying to Vercel:
1. Enable Web Analytics in the Vercel dashboard (Analytics tab)
2. Deploy the application
3. The `/_vercel/insights/*` routes will be automatically added after deployment
4. Analytics data will appear in the dashboard after initial visitors access the site
